Description:
SPECTACULAR CRANBOURNE EAST LIFESTYLE!
Desirably positioned in an urban growth corridor within close proximity of Hunt Club Shopping Centre and Cranbourne Primary School, this two-acre hobby farm represents both wonderful lifestyle and subdivision potential (STCA).
Served by bore water and rainwater tanks, this highly-productive land is divided into three main paddocks with fully fencing, horse stables and ample shedding. The existing residence offers versatile interiors accentuated by three well-proportioned bedrooms, family bathroom and functional kitchen with quality appliances. Multiple living zones ensure space for growing families to relax and unwind. This sprawling residence offers every convenience, with added benefits incorporating heating, cooling and a secure lock-up garage for vehicles and farm machinery.
Situated on the doorstep of major arterials and minutes from local shops (Hunt Club Shopping Centre, Springhill Shopping Centre and Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre), schools (Cranbourne East Primary Secondary and Casey Grammar) and within easy commute of Melbourne CBD, this is the ultimate location with so many advantages.
Enquire now for further details and to arrange inspection!
Insights: 40 Mayfield Road, Cranbourne East VIC 3977 was last sold in 2019 and 153 other 4 bedroom house in Cranbourne East have recently been sold.

Description:
Fantastic Family Living with Extras!
Situated in close proximity to all amenities including schools and shops is this fantastic family home. A must see for anyone wanting a quality property in an unbeatable location.
Boasting large bedrooms, master with WIR, the spacious ensuite is complimented by an extended shower base and dual shower heads. A well-appointed kitchen overlooks a very generous size lounge and dining area, with the benefits of a rumpus to the rear, elevated ceilings, timber floorboards and ducted heating and refrigerated air-conditioning throughout.

Situated in this prized location, on a large allotment of 602sq metres with double lock up garage, this fantastic family home is set amongst impeccably maintained gardens and is a must see.

Description:
What a spot to live!
This well maintained ex display home on a big level block consists of a monster master bedroom with full ensuite and walk in robe. The other two large bedrooms have double robes. The neat kitchen has a pantry, gas stove, electric oven, rangehood , dishwasher, double sink and ample bench space. The large meals/living area has direct access to the outside of the house. In addition is a formal lounge and an expansive rumpus room which also has direct access to the outside of the house. Other features include ducted heating and evaporative cooling. The double garage under roof line has an auto roller door and a rear roller door that enables vehicle access through to the back yard that has a relatively new steel garage workshop.
This home is in walking distance to the Selandra Rise Shopping Centre, Local Bus stop, Cascade Wetlands, parks and walking tracks. The property is handy to St. Peters Secondary Collage, St. Theresa's Primary School, Cranbourne East Primary School and Secondary Collage. A short drive away is either Cranbourne or Berwick Railway Stations. In the precinct are the extensive sporting facilities of Casey Fields that has modern facilities for a huge range of sports.

Description:
A FAMILY FAVORITE
CRANBOURNE EAST: Located within walking distance to Casey Fields is this once in a lifetime opportunity to own this quality home built by Creation Homes. Set on a block of approximately 400 square meters, this home is a must-see as it will surely impress the fussiest of buyers.
Four bedrooms with a generous sized master comes complete with a full en-suite that includes a single vanity while the other three bedrooms are conveniently located in close proximity to the second shower and toilet.
The hostess kitchen is a chef's dream and is complete with quality stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, 600mm range hood, 4-burner gas cook top, laminate bench tops, tiled splash back with ample overhead storage and bench space. All of this overlooking the separate meals and living area.
The outdoors is like a blank canvas waiting for someone with a bit of flair and imagination. There is heaps of room to accommodate a pergola as well as room for the kids to kick a footy, all of this in an enclosed backyard.
Young families with children will be blown away with the amenities on offer, like sports fields, council reserves, parks and open spaces. Casey Fields is a short stroll away which has plenty on offer, not to miss the swimming pools, library and the community center all walking distance from this home. If you do want to miss out please make note of the inspection times.

Residing within the much-admired Livingston Estate' is this well presented Porter Davis home. Accommodation needs are well and truly met with a generous master bedroom with full ensuite and walk in robe, followed by two remaining bedrooms both with DBIR and benefiting from the spacious family bathroom.

Description:
THE BEST THE HUNT CLUB HAS TO OFFER!
Sitting on a generous 585sqm approx. is this well presented home located in the heart of the Hunt Club Estate. This family home consisting of 3 great sized bedrooms serviced by a central family bathroom, separate toilet, all with BIR's one with a great study nook and both with ceiling fans. Master suite with en-suite and large WIR.
The property has a family friendly layout offering a large front lounge/formal dining flowing into the spacious open plan family living and meals area with lovely gas fireplace as a centerpiece. At the central hub of the home is the stunning kitchen with s/s appliances, 600mm wall oven, dishwasher, island bench with breakfast bar as well as plenty of cupboard and bench space.
The outdoor of this home offers a great place to enjoy time with friends and family featuring a huge concreted undercover pitched roof alfresco area to entertain all your family and friends all year round. To top it off there is great size grassed backyard for the kids and pets to play, garden shed, side access and drive through roller door access to the rear yard via the 2.5 car garage with built in storage and custom built workbench.
Other extras in the property include: huge laundry with oversized storage cupboards, ducted heating, down lights, tiled throughout, low maintenance gardens back and front, rainwater tank for garden watering, fern garden and much much more!
The property is located in a quiet cul-de-sac street and centrally located to wetlands and walking tracks plus within short walking distance to the Hunt Club Village Shopping Centre complex, Cranbourne East Primary and Secondary Schools, child care centre and public transport.
Homes in this location are selling fast so be quick to inspect. A must add to your open home list!

Description:
UNDER CONTACT/ UNDER OFFER
CRANBOURNE EAST: This home will not disappoint! Stella location, this fantastic home is walking distance to both Hunt Club Schools and a short distance to the Hunt Club village. The sensational floorplan oozes comfort and class from the minute your walk in the front door allowing you the opportunity to literally unpack and relax
The floorplan features 4 genuine robed bedrooms plus a good size study that can be doubled up as formal front living area. The master bedroom is complete with walk-in robe and full ensuite. Bedrooms 2, 3 and 4 are all nicely distributed to the rear of the home and is in a good proximity to the family bathroom.
The hostess kitchen is the central hub of the home and is finished with a good amount of cupboard space and bench space, glass splash back, stone bench tops, quality appliances including 900mm free standing oven and gas cooktop, rangehood, dishwasher. All this overlooking the great sized family meals zone with sliding door access outside
Take advantage of the 2 separate living zones making year-round formal and informal entertaining a breeze! Relax with a good movie and glass of your finest wine in the rear rumpus living area and the carefree day to day living will be enjoyed in the kitchen/meals family zone.
Added internal extras include, retrofit double glaze windows to portion of the home, home ventilation system for clean air year round, Daikin refrigerated heating and cooling, downlights and a mix of tile and carpet floor coverings and neutral colour tones throughout
Step outside and be greeted by a sensational street scape offering a modern facade and a neat, tidy and low maintenance front landscaping. A lengthy concrete driveway leads to the remote double lock up garage, that has internal access plus rear access to the back. The outdoor living space is second to none, with a huge pitched roof concreted pergola with lights, outdoor heaters ceiling fan and the option for you to have a TV set up if you wish, this will defiantly make outdoor living a year-round feature. The kids and pets will have a blast with the great sized backyard with additional garden shed and great kids cubby house.
The cherry on top of this already amazing house is the 8 solar panels that will surely keep those ever-creeping electrical bills down to a minimum.
The Hunt Club is a multi-award winning estate offering numerous parks, wetlands, walking and bicycle paths as well as a complete range of childcare, primary (Cranbourne East Primary) and secondary schools (Cranbourne East Secondary College). Buses weave through the estate making the newly built shopping centre complete with Woolworths & Aldi easily accessible. Recycled water, high speed broadband and environmentally friendly designs are all part of the estate.
Don't waste your time with a frustrating building process! It's all here waiting for you and you don't even need to lift a finger!

Description:
UNDER CONTRACT/ UNDER OFFER!
Cranbourne East: If you are looking for a great home with all of the creature comforts then this home is yours for the taking! This sensational floorplan oozes comfort and class from the minute your walk in the front door allowing you the opportunity to literally unpack and relax!
The floorplan features 4 genuine robed bedrooms on offer plus study nook. The master bedroom is complete with walk-in robe and full ensuite with dual vanities. Bedrooms 2, 3 and 4 are all nicely distributed throughout the top floor & in a good proximity to the family bathroom.
If you are a firm believer that the kitchen is where the heart of the home is then you won't be disappointed. Complete with all of the mod cons there are stone bench tops, plenty of cupboard space plus quality stainless steel appliances including a stainless steel 600mm cook top, oven & dishwasher, glass splashback and walk in pantry. All this overlooking the great size kitchen meals area with sliding door access to the back yard.
Added extras include, ducted heating, evaporative air conditioning, powder room downstairs, neutral tones, quality floor coverings throughout including carpets and tiles and to top it off solar hot water.
Step outside and enjoy the great extended decked alfresco area, perfect for entertaining all year round. The low maintenance landscaping means little upkeep but still plenty of room for the kids and pets to play
The great street scape immediately ads to the overall appeal and includes a 2 car garage with internal access and porched entry just to top it off.
Sensational location nearby to family parkland and established shopping facilities together. Sport and recreation facilities & public transport are all close by. There is also easy access to both Fountain Gate and the Cranbourne Park shopping centre, whist you can take full advantage of the immediate freeway access if you happen to work in the CBD!

Description:
Modern Home Oozing Class & Sophistication
Intelligent design combined with clean lines, neutral tones and contemporary finishes make this home the right choice. Whether it's your first property, an investment or your forever home, it ticks all the boxes.
The kitchen/dining/family area is light and airy with an open floor plan, large windows/sliding doors and feature lighting, including downlights. The kitchen is functional yet stylish, complete with a stone bench top including breakfast bar, high-end stainless-steel appliances including a dishwasher and a 5-burner gas stove top, walk in pantry and more. Complimented with an alfresco, this space gives you the opportunity to enjoy outdoor family meals or entertaining guests year-round.
A secluded family room is the ideal chill zone for movie nights or relaxing at the end of a long day. The master bedroom is inviting and comfortable, complete with a fully kitted out WIR, and en suite including a double vanity and large shower. The 3 remaining bedrooms are spacious complete with BIRs, carpeted floors and large windows. The family bathroom is functional and sophisticated with a separate bath and shower, high-quality fittings and a statement vanity.
Main features include:
- Outstanding finishes and attention to detail
- Unique, modern design
- Alfresco for year-round outdoor living
- Open-plan kitchen/dining/family linked to alfresco
- Four spacious bedrooms with carpeted floors
- Two elegant bathrooms with separate WC and laundry
- Ceramic tiling and durable carpet throughout
- Quality lighting around the home
- Central heating and split units for temperature control
- Double garage with internal and rear yard access
- Extensive, easy to maintain landscaped garden
Located in a quiet court in a lovely pocket of Cranbourne East, this home is close to all the amenities you will need including parks, schools and more.
This one of a kind property will get snapped up quickly, so book an inspection with our team today!
